Video clips of a youngster's hilarious impressions of Kaizer Chiefs coach Steve Komphela have been doing the rounds on social media. And guess what? The Komphela impersonator‚ Simangaliso Mdluli‚ is‚ in fact‚ a Chiefs fan. He hails from Vryheid in KwaZulu-Natal. Like Komphela‚ originally a teacher by profession‚ Mdluli is studying towards a Bachelor of Education at the University of Johannesburg. Komphela holds a teacher's diploma from Tshiya College of Education in QwaQwa‚ Free State. The Robert Marawa impersonator in the video is Mdluli's friend‚ Nyameko Hadebe.